<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.4.3">
<l>vavvit tuḻāyataṉmēl ceṉṟa taṉineñcam</l>
<l>cevvi yaṟiyātu niṟkuṅkol nittilaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>pavvat tiraiyulavu pullāṇi kaitoḻutēṉ</l>
<l>teyvac cilaiyāṟkeṉ cintainōy ceppumiṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will [my] lonely heart, which raced to his tulasī, grasping at [it],</l>
<l>Stay [there] without considering [my] plight? I worship, hands [joined],</l>
<l>In Pullāṇi, where pearls ride in the foaming waves.</l>
<l>Please tell the one with the divine bow of the malady of my mind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
